gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d9e3dbaf1164fad29ee3084ec70eb25bf77395","tid":426234,"uid":94799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629c5865cfaa850e6a77b394a2d4a42c97a528de","tid":426234,"uid":40042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下年5月會第一次衝出亞洲去東歐做老襯加旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,大概十日時間. 追左好多post 後draft 左個行程plan出黎,請巴/絲打幫幫手狠評吓會唔會出事 or 有咩推介餐廳一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nHKG(18/5) &gt; <br />\n<br />\nVienna(19/5) &gt; Hallstatt(19/5,stay) &gt; <br />\n<br />\nCesky Krumlov(20/5,stay) &gt; <br />\n<br />\nPrague(21-23/5,stay) &gt;  [23/5 會係Prague 影一日相後凌晨巴士走]<br />\n<br />\nBudapest(24-28/5,stay)  [追歐遊post 好多巴絲打都極力推介,會否太長]&gt; <br />\n<br />\nBUD to HKG(28-29/5,~15:00)<br />\n<br />\n利申:機票酒店車票咩都未訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個星期前去完budapest 我覺得冇想像中咁正<br />\n講靚 唔夠wien同prague<br />\n講平 又唔係話平到笑 講特色我又諗唔到有啲咩<br />\n我覺得你留5日好似多左d <br />\n如果你去到 有一日無野做 可以去佢附近小鎮 szetendre <br />\n我覺得幾舒服 慢慢行 可以留3-5小時"},{"pid":"8d545431834d8d94fb43bd68e378d1ec73ba06b6","tid":426234,"uid":57982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴絲打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Update 吓今星期先,<br />\n<br />\n今星期訂左機票同埋Hallstatt酒店,唔想坐車出去,要挨貴酒店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間野叫Heritage Hotel Hallstatt, D comment 都幾伏吓有冇巴絲住過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外, 會係果到留多日去睇five fingers, 睇相真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHKG to VIE (18-19/5,~08:30) &gt; <br />\n<br />\nVienna to Hallstatt [by OBB] (19-21/5,stay 2 days) &gt;<br />\n<br />\nCesky Krumlov(21-22/5,stay 1 night) &gt; <br />\n<br />\nPrague(22-24/5,stay 2 nights) &gt; <br />\n<br />\nBudapest(24-28/5,stay 3 nights) &gt; BUD to HKG (28-29/5,~15:00)"}]}